{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Valor Of Man is a  tactical RPG with roguelike mechanics where enemies react to your actions. Lead your party of heroes as you anticipate and outsmart your enemies. Make careful decisions as you forge your path to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br>  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699280/extras/unpredictable.png?t=1739269050\" />Death is tired of reaping souls all day, and enlists you, Alistair, as his avatar of destruction. Explore an intriguing narrative as you throw the world into chaos in your quest to stop the Perpetual Cycle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699280/extras/1-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1739269050\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemies respond to your attacks with original Reactions. Use your wits and arsenal to best over <strong>60 foes including elites and bosses</strong>, each with distinctive behaviour and mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unleash devastating critical hits that uniquely affect each enemy by disabling their <strong>special behaviours, buffs or abilities.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699280/extras/2-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1739269050\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your party from <strong>12 hero classes across 4 archetypes</strong>. Set up deadly combos, discover powerful synergies and wreak havoc on your enemies with <strong>250+ hero abilities, 250+ items and 150+ game-changing artifacts</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a <strong>Roguelike adventure</strong> where, after each win or loss, you unlock new gear and abilities to empower your heroes in future runs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699280/extras/3-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1739269050\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enhanced by <strong>dynamic map generation</strong>, a 3 Chapter story, and varied enemies, each run is shaped by your choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adjustable difficulty spans across <strong>10 Valor Levels</strong>, progressively unlocking new story chapters while intensifying the challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>About us:</strong>\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We are Traian and Florian, 2 brothers, who love playing and making games, and together we have created Legacy Forge Studio. Driven by passion to craft innovative gameplay experiences with unique mechanics, we take elements from different mediums (ex: board games) and implement them in video games.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699280/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739269050","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699280/page.bg.jpg?t=1739269050","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699280/72f682c1dbb12a0874b9c531dcaca2745a00d10d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739269050","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699280/72f682c1dbb12a0874b9c531dcaca2745a00d10d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739269050","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Valor of Man may contain content not appropriate for all ages, or may not be appropriate for viewing at work: General Mature Content."},"demos":[{"appid":3222870,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Valor Of Man is a  tactical RPG with roguelike mechanics where enemies react to your actions. 